Three-in-a-row 

- Three in a row award the user with 60 points

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Wrap

- Making a 'wrap' awards the user with 200 points.
In order to get 'wrap' bonus, the user needs to get 5 jellies 
in a 'L' or 'T' shape.

- Matching a 'wrap' gives 540 points plus 60 for each candy destroyed.

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Stripe

- 'Stripe' is achieved by getting 4 of the same color in a row.
By doing this, the user receives 120 points.

- Matching a 'stripe' will cause a blast across the board, the same way as the stripes on the candy point, and each candy in the path of the stripe gives 60 points.

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Colour bomb

- Making a 'colour bomb' will give you 200 points.
In order to get 'colour bomb' bonus, the user needs to get 6 jellies

- Matching a 'colour bomb' gives 1200 plus 60 for every candy destroyed.

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: 'Jelly squares' are worth 1000 points each, so if you make a match of 3 candies on top of jelly you will get 3000 points for the jelly, plus 60 for the match of 3.
